notesStmt.note: This conversation takes place during a break at a mathematics conference. S6 asks for S7's opinion on the definition of strict pseudo-convexity for a Lipschitz domain. The speakers seem to be acquainted (though not too well). S4 is the session chair and only appears at the end, when he calls people to come in for the next talk. S8 is the next speaker and only joins in briefly.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
